title: ChinaNet Online boosts revenues  narrows loss in Q3
content: ChinaNet Online   NASDAQ CNET  has logged Q3 earnings that saw improvement in gross profit and narrower operating and net losses  Net loss came to  1 5M vs  a loss of  2 1M in the year ago quarter  Gross profit improved 39 8  to  2M  Despite a company pivot into higher margin businesses than TV advertising  gross margin fell to 17  from 17 1  due to an increase in lower margin revenues from search engine marketing services  Cash outflows from operations for the nine months were  1 9M  the company has  1 2M in cash and equivalents  working capital of  9 8M and a current ration of 2 3 to 1  Conference call to come tomorrow at 8 30 a m  ET  Press Release
